<arggraph id="micro_c067" topic_id="charge_for_plastic_bags" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[The problem with plastic bags is they are not biodegradable]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[and they pollute the environment.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[In order to encourage the use for reusable bags it would be ideal to charge for the plastic bags]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[to provide an incentive for using them.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[There are those who would say that not everyone can afford reusable bags]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[but that is not a valid argument]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[because the plastic bags will still be available for only a few pennies.]]></edu>
